				<span class="author">
					<a href="http://en.gravatar.com/site/signup" class="gravatar"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=1f0067bce6eeec9491fd805593106604&size=31&rating=R&d=identicon" alt="" /></a>					<div>
